name: The Weird, Strange, Odd, Bizarre and Not so Normal day of KEITH
name_original: The Weird, Strange, Odd, Bizarre and Not so Normal day of KEITH
description:
The Wierd, Strange, Odd, Bizzare and Not So Normal Day of Keith is a student-designed and produced game made in Unity. The Team at Duck Duck games will be presenting the game at PAX Aus 2022 as part of the Swinburne University stall. 

Office Worker Keith's day started out pretty normal, but good stories don't end that way. Enjoy as Keith tries to make sense of his bizarre surroundings, Odd characters, Strange events and Weird world.
